    637  f2f4							; CheckCollision - player vs the entity on the player's floor.
    638  f2f4							;   cone  -> +1 to the BCD score, entity consumed.
    639  f2f4							;   skull -> game over (freeze + red background).
    640  f2f4							;-------------------------------------------------------------
